wiki.summary: “SPIT IN MY FACE!” is the long-awaited single from the young artist ThxSoMuch. First previewed on TikTok as a snippet on October 8, 2022 and blew up just eight days later on the sixteenth. The song was previewed along with other snippets like “Imperfect Girl”, “ONLY NEED MY BABY! (SMOAGT)” and “HOW YOU ALWAYS LOOK SO GOOD?”. “SPIT IN MY FACE!” is about how ThxSoMuch is falling deep into a toxic relationship, to the point were he’d bleed for her, but with no emotion back. Read more on Last.fm.
